{"tid":1305922,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE會考大不同","createTime":"2019-07-11T03:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T03:45:18.000Z","uid":129861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"45c189d8c66cecdaf5b9a2bf25d3f069ab047a69","tid":1305922,"uid":129861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:35:48.000Z","msg":"DSE跟會考除了學制的不同外，最重要是社會環境的改變，以前會考若英文不及格，便注定與專上教育無緣，出來社會工作是常態。能通往專上教育的途徑十分之小，就算有亦只有夜間課程，從工業學院﹝現在的IVE﹞報讀一年夜間的銜接課程，之後便能報讀工業學院證書課程。<br />\n證書&rarr;高級證書&rarr;高級文憑&rarr;學位，若一切順利需歷時十年。現在升學的途徑可以說是五花八門，甚至可以說是能保證進身專上教育。當年小弟會考成績換算為DSE如下：﹝預設通識科能合格﹞<br />\n第一年：中文2  英文U 數學3 通識2 化學2<br />\n重考：中文2  英文1 數學4 通識2 化學3<br />\n上網查詢過，重考的成績已經能報讀公大學位課程"},{"pid":"4c05c6d790d1657abd8d32047aee5ae84aeff437","tid":1305922,"uid":263464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:45:18.000Z","msg":"7.11 - 梁烈士公眾告別禮 - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnfkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=e5789242\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/leung711</a><br />\n7.11 - 油尖旺區議會夢遊 - <a href=\"http://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_dc711&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnfkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=25402943\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/ytm_dc711</a><br />\n7.12 - <span style=\"color: gold;\">6.12一周月行動</span> - <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hklsd/photos/a.101378395784/10156221199385785/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhklsd%2Fphotos%2Fa.101378395784%2F10156221199385785%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnfkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=a46ae4d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hklsd/photos/a.101378395784/10156221199385785/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n7.13 - 全民中銀撳錢 - <a href=\"https://t.me/loveBOC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FloveBOC&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnfkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=bb23e73b\" ta